metadata.name: KinerjaPay Corp
metadata.description: KinerjaPay Corp. operates an e-commerce platform in Indonesia. The company's platform, KinerjaPay IP, an e-wallet service for bill transfers and online shopping; and allows top-up phone credit for users. It also provides KMALL, a virtual marketplace for B2B and B2C online transactions; and KGAMES that develops games. The company was formerly known as Solarflex Corp and changed its name to KinerjaPay Corp on February 2016. KinerjaPay Corp. was founded in 2010 and is based in Medan, Indonesia.
